    <item>
      <title>政策乐观情绪推动中国股市回吐早盘涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/chinese-stocks-rally-after-top-leaders-signal-bolder-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市上涨失去动力，表明投资者希望看到政策制定者在做出多年来最坚定的恢复经济增长的承诺后采取具体措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/chinese-stocks-rally-after-top-leaders-signal-bolder-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 01:32:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
